  <h2>Zen Mode</h2>
  <p>Press <strong>i</strong> on your keyboard to toggle all interface elements and admire the magic squares without distraction.</p>


  <h2>Single Modal</h2>
  <p><strong>Double click</strong> with your mouse on any magic square to see a full screen version of it.</p>

  <h2>Printing</h2>
  <p>Press <strong>p</strong> on your keyboard to toggle print preview mode. You can then choose to print this view by pressing <strong>ctrl p</strong> or right clicking anywhere within the screen and choosing <strong>Print...</strong>.</p>
  <p>Please note that printing uses your settings, so for a light printer-friendly version change to day-mode or adjust the colour settings manually before entering print preview. <emph>Printing order 5s in bulk is not recommended and slightly broken.</emph></p>


  <h2>Publications</h2>

  <p><a href="https://www.scienceopen.com/document?vid=ec68f646-d76e-4961-986e-1aa83123d146">Creative Visualisation of Magic Squares</a> paper for EVA2020 London.</p>

